snippet.title: Target Practice with Tana in Fire Emblem: Oops, All Archers!
snippet.description:
#fireemblem #tana #romhack
Does FE8 become hard if everyone is an archer? Nope. 
But powertripping with Tana was still fun.
Link to the hack: https://feuniverse.us/t/fe8-oops-all-archers-v3-0-beta-new-bosses/15253
This could've come out a bit sooner but neither me nor my laptop like the summer heat :U
